Package energy.usef.core.workflow.transformer

Transformer classes for the workflow.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AcknoledgementStatusTransformer
    Transformer class in charge of the conversion of the AcknowledgementStatus to its related DTO.
    DispositionAcceptedDisputedTransformer
    Transformer class for the DispositionAcceptedDisputedDto enumeration.
    DispositionTransformer
    Transformer class for transforming between different disposition types.
    FlexOfferTransformer
    Transformer class in charge of the mapping of PtuFlexOffer from the database to PtuFlexOfferDto objects and FlexOfferDto objects.
    FlexOrderTransformer
    Transformer class in charge of the transformation of PtuFlexOrder to FlexOrderDto.
    FlexRequestTransformer
    Transformer class for handling Flex related transformations.
    MeterDataTransformer
    Transformer class to map XML generated Meter Data object to DTOs.
    MeterEventTransformer
    Transformer class for entities related to the MeterEvent xml entity.
    PrognosisTransformer
    Transformer class for for transforming prognosis related objects.
    PtuContainerTransformer
    Transformer class for for transforming PtuContainer to PtuContainerDto.
    SettlementTransformer
    Transformer class for Settlement-related items.
    USEFRoleTransformer
    Transformer class transforming the USEFRole enumeration to its related DTO enumeration (USEFRoleDto).
